# CI/CD - {{ project_name }}

## Overview

All CI/CD runs on **GitHub Actions** with **path-based triggers** - each platform's workflow only runs when its files change.

## Workflows

| Workflow | Trigger Paths | What It Does |
|----------|--------------|--------------|
{% if "backend" in platforms %}| `backend.yml` | `backend/**`, `shared/**` | Gradle test + build, Docker push to Azure ACR, deploy to Container Apps |
{% endif %}{% if "user-web-app" in platforms %}| `user-web-app.yml` | `user-web-app/**`, `shared/**` | npm lint + typecheck + build, deploy to Cloudflare via OpenNext |
{% endif %}{% if "admin-web-portal" in platforms %}| `admin-web-portal.yml` | `admin-web-portal/**`, `shared/**` | npm lint + typecheck + build, deploy to Cloudflare via OpenNext |
{% endif %}{% if "android" in platforms %}| `android.yml` | `android/**`, `shared/**` | Gradle test + assembleDebug, Fastlane deploy on tags |
{% endif %}{% if "ios" in platforms %}| `ios.yml` | `ios/**`, `shared/**` | xcodebuild test (macOS runner), Fastlane deploy on tags |
{% endif %}| `api-contracts.yml` | `shared/api-contracts/**` | Validate OpenAPI spec |

## Required GitHub Secrets

### Azure
| Secret | Description |
|--------|-------------|
| `AZURE_CREDENTIALS` | Service principal JSON |
| `AZURE_CONTAINER_REGISTRY` | ACR login server |
| `AZURE_CONTAINER_APP_NAME` | Container App name |
| `AZURE_RESOURCE_GROUP` | Resource group |

{% if "user-web-app" in platforms or "admin-web-portal" in platforms %}
### Cloudflare
| Secret | Description |
|--------|-------------|
| `CLOUDFLARE_ACCOUNT_ID` | Account ID |
| `CLOUDFLARE_API_TOKEN` | API token |
{% endif %}

{% if "android" in platforms %}
### Android
| Secret | Description |
|--------|-------------|
| `ANDROID_KEYSTORE_BASE64` | Signing keystore (base64) |
| `ANDROID_KEYSTORE_PASSWORD` | Keystore password |
| `ANDROID_KEY_ALIAS` | Key alias |
| `ANDROID_KEY_PASSWORD` | Key password |
| `GOOGLE_PLAY_SERVICE_ACCOUNT_JSON` | Play Console service account |
{% endif %}

{% if "ios" in platforms %}
### iOS
| Secret | Description |
|--------|-------------|
| `MATCH_PASSWORD` | Fastlane match encryption password |
| `APP_STORE_CONNECT_API_KEY` | App Store Connect API key JSON |
{% endif %}
